---
import HeroImage from "../assets/pitcairn-aviation-hangar-space.jpg";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
---

<div class="mx-auto mt-32 max-w-7xl px-6 sm:mt-40">
  <div
    class="mx-auto flex max-w-2xl flex-col items-end justify-between gap-16 lg:mx-0 lg:max-w-none lg:flex-row"
  >
    <div class="w-full lg:max-w-lg lg:flex-auto">
      <h2
        class="text-main-color brightness-125 text-base font-bold leading-none uppercase fade-in duration-500 opacity-0 delay-100"
      >
        AIRCRAFT HANGAR SOLUTIONS
      </h2>
      <p
        class="py-2 text-4xl font-bold font-paragraph max-w-md fade-in duration-500 opacity-0 delay-200"
      >
        Premium Aircraft Protection at Heritage Field Airport
      </p>
      <p class="mt-6 text-xl/8 text-gray-600">
        Your aircraft deserves the best. Pitcairn Aviation offers <strong
          >climate-controlled, secure hangars</strong
        > with 24/7 monitored access, gated security, and direct taxiway convenience.
        Whether you need an overnight stop or long-term storage, our facilities provide
        <strong>military-grade protection</strong> with premium FBO amenities.
      </p>
      <Image
        src={HeroImage}
        class="mt-16 aspect-6/5 w-full bg-gray-50 object-cover lg:aspect-auto lg:h-138"
        alt="Private aircraft in Pitcairn Aviation's heated hangar"
      />
    </div>
    <div class="w-full lg:max-w-xl lg:flex-auto">
      <h3 class="sr-only">Why Choose Our Hangars?</h3>
      <ul class="-my-8 divide-y divide-gray-100">
        <li class="py-8">
          <dl class="relative flex flex-wrap gap-x-3">
            <dt class="sr-only">Feature</dt>
            <dd
              class="w-full flex-none text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight py-2 text-gray-900"
            >
              <a href="#">
                Year-Round Climate Control
                <span aria-hidden="true" class="absolute inset-0"></span>
              </a>
            </dd>
            <dt class="sr-only">Description</dt>
            <dd class="mt-2 w-full flex-none text-base/7 text-gray-600">
              <strong>Heated hangar bays</strong> prevent cold-weather damage and
              protect sensitive avionics. Our temperature-regulated environment eliminates
              moisture buildup and extreme temperature swings.
            </dd>
          </dl>
        </li>
        <li class="py-8">
          <dl class="relative flex flex-wrap gap-x-3">
            <dt class="sr-only">Feature</dt>
            <dd
              class="w-full flex-none text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight py-2 text-gray-900"
            >
              <a href="#">
                Flexible Rental Terms
                <span aria-hidden="true" class="absolute inset-0"></span>
              </a>
            </dd>
            <dt class="sr-only">Description</dt>
            <dd class="mt-2 w-full flex-none text-base/7 text-gray-600">
              <strong>No long-term contracts</strong> – choose from hourly, overnight,
              weekly, or monthly options. Perfect for transient pilots and local
              owners alike.
            </dd>
          </dl>
        </li>
        <li class="py-8">
          <dl class="relative flex flex-wrap gap-x-3">
            <dt class="sr-only">Feature</dt>
            <dd
              class="w-full flex-none text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight py-2 text-gray-900"
            >
              <a href="#">
                Military-Grade Security
                <span aria-hidden="true" class="absolute inset-0"></span>
              </a>
            </dd>
            <dt class="sr-only">Description</dt>
            <dd class="mt-2 w-full flex-none text-base/7 text-gray-600">
              <strong>24/7 surveillance</strong>, biometric gate access, and
              on-site staff. Your aircraft is protected by the same systems used
              at corporate FBOs – at general aviation prices.
            </dd>
          </dl>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <div class="mt-8 flex border-t border-gray-100 pt-8">
        <a
          href="/hangar-rental-form"
          class="btn-primary fade-in duration-500 opacity-0"
          >Reserve Your Hangar Today <span aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span></a
        >
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="bg-white py-24 sm:py-32">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-12">
        More Than Just Storage
      </h3>
      <div
        class="mx-auto grid max-w-2xl grid-cols-1 gap-8 overflow-hidden lg:mx-0 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-4"
      >
        <div>
          <div
            class="flex items-center text-sm/6 font-semibold text-main-color"
          >
            <svg
              viewBox="0 0 4 4"
              aria-hidden="true"
              class="mr-4 size-1 flex-none"
            >
              <circle r="2" cx="2" cy="2" fill="currentColor"></circle>
            </svg>
            Jet-Ready Facilities
          </div>
          <p
            class="mt-6 text-lg/8 font-semibold tracking-tight py-2 text-gray-900"
          >
            Upgraded for Larger Aircraft
          </p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-base/7 text-gray-600">
            Reinforced doors and expanded bays accommodate <strong
              >light jets and turboprops</strong
            > up to 30,000 lbs. Improved drainage prevents water intrusion.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <div
            class="flex items-center text-sm/6 font-semibold text-main-color"
          >
            <svg
              viewBox="0 0 4 4"
              aria-hidden="true"
              class="mr-4 size-1 flex-none"
            >
              <circle r="2" cx="2" cy="2" fill="currentColor"></circle>
            </svg>
            White-Glove Ground Support
          </div>
          <p
            class="mt-6 text-lg/8 font-semibold tracking-tight py-2 text-gray-900"
          >
            Expert Aircraft Handling
          </p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-base/7 text-gray-600">
            Our <strong>FAA-certified line crew</strong> provides GPU hookups, tow
            services, and battery jumps. Vintage aircraft specialists available.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <div
            class="flex items-center text-sm/6 font-semibold text-main-color"
          >
            <svg
              viewBox="0 0 4 4"
              aria-hidden="true"
              class="mr-4 size-1 flex-none"
            >
              <circle r="2" cx="2" cy="2" fill="currentColor"></circle>
            </svg>
            Pilot-Centric Amenities
          </div>
          <p
            class="mt-6 text-lg/8 font-semibold tracking-tight py-2 text-gray-900"
          >
            Business-Class Comfort
          </p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-base/7 text-gray-600">
            <strong>Private conference rooms</strong>, high-speed Wi-Fi, and
            crew lounges. Complimentary refreshments while you wait.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <div
            class="flex items-center text-sm/6 font-semibold text-main-color"
          >
            <svg
              viewBox="0 0 4 4"
              aria-hidden="true"
              class="mr-4 size-1 flex-none"
            >
              <circle r="2" cx="2" cy="2" fill="currentColor"></circle>
            </svg>
            Instant Fuel Access
          </div>
          <p
            class="mt-6 text-lg/8 font-semibold tracking-tight py-2 text-gray-900"
          >
            Phillips 66 Fuel Station
          </p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-base/7 text-gray-600">
            <strong>24/7 self-serve AvGas/Jet-A</strong> just steps from your hangar.
            Major credit cards accepted.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
